text:
someone really need to give a guide on what to bring when explore, gura has way too many unnecessary items in her inventory. 

normally i brought
1) stone pickaxe and a iron pickaxe/diamond pickaxe(which ever you can afford)
2) a stack of torches, very important
3)a stack of wood log/wood plank (which ever you like)
4)a stack of food or so
5)a stack of cobblestone
6)sword that you prefer, i usually go for stone sword


with wood plank and stone, i can make a crafting table and make infinite stone pickaxe and stone sword as long i have wood in my inventory. there is no lack of coals under the surface, so you can make torch too. you can leave the crafting table at where it is cause they are very cheap to make. if you are feeling lucky or dare, you can leave the cobblestone out too, but i found it to be safer to bring a stack of cobblestone.

you can bring a bow and some arrows when you are in nether cause those ghasts are just too annoying. but for pro player, they either beat the ghast with sword or just run away still like a pro.
